76
00:05:40,020 --> 00:05:42,519
Jangan pandang rendah terhadap saya.

77
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:45,019
Kerana sayalah satu-satunya Detektif Kogorou Mouri.

78
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:46,819
Maaf.

79
00:05:46,820 --> 00:05:47,920
Maafkan saya.

80
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:52,219
Cepat betul kamu pulang.

81
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:55,719
Kami ingin pergi lebih lama,

82
