125
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:08,019
Saya boleh tanya Encik Honjou jika dia boleh tukar ia kepada ucapan biasa.

126
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:09,520
Itu idea yang bagus.

127
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,719
Conan.

128
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:24,620
Kamu masih sakit perut?

129
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,220
Tidak terlalu teruk.

130
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:32,219
Tetapi saya mahu pergi ke tandas lagi.

131
00:09:32,220 --> 00:09:33,620
Conan.

132
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:39,519
Encik Honjou, boleh kita tukar skit Encik Mouri

133
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:41,819
