148
00:11:09,499 --> 00:11:11,798
Itu Encik Hirose,

149
00:11:11,799 --> 00:11:13,798
presiden Persatuan Wain Kebangsaan

150
00:11:13,799 --> 00:11:15,699
dan tetamu kehormat pada malam ini.

151
00:11:16,699 --> 00:11:19,099
Itu pingat dari Perancis.

